---
import CornellNote from '../../components/CornellNote.astro';

// LaTeX constants for math accuracy
const limInf = "$\\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to \\infty}$";
---

<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>실전 연습 - 무한대 극한</title>
		<!-- KaTeX (Safe CDN) -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css">
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js"></script>
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js"></script>
		<style>
			body {
				background-color: #e0e0e0;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 20px;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
			}
			.solution {
				color: #444;
				background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
				padding: 10px 15px;
				border-left: 3px solid #ccc;
				margin: 10px 0;
			}
			/* Mobile Optimization for Type Headers */
			@media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
				.type-header {
					flex-direction: column !important;
					align-items: flex-start !important;
					gap: 10px;
				}
				.problem-link {
					margin-left: 0 !important;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<CornellNote title="무한대로 갈 때의 극한" chapter="Chapter 01 Practice">
			
			<div slot="cues">
				<p style="margin: 0; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a1a;">🚀 해결 전략 체크리스트</p>
				<ul style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 18px; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.6; color: #444;">
					<li>{ "식의 형태 파악 ($\\frac{\\infty}{\\infty}$ 또는 $\\infty-\\infty$)" }</li>
					<li>분모와 분자의 최고차항 비교</li>
					<li>무리식이 있다면 유리화 검토</li>
					<li>극한값이 상수일 때 차수 추론</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<section>
				<!-- Type 01 -->
				<div class="type-section" id="type01">
					<div class="type-header" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 15px;">
						<h4 style="margin: 0; color: #1a1a1a; border-bottom: 2px solid royalblue; display: inline-block; padding-bottom: 5px;">
							유형 01. 유리함수
						</h4>
						<a href="/wiki/chapter01/types/type01/" class="problem-link">연습 ✏️</a>
					</div>
					<p>다음 극한값을 구하시오.</p>
					<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.4rem; margin: var(--base-grid) 0;">
						{limInf} { "$ \\frac{3x^2 - 5x + 1}{x^2 + 2} $" }
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Type 02 -->
				<div class="type-section" id="type02">
					<div class="type-header" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 15px;">
						<h4 style="margin: 0; color: #1a1a1a; border-bottom: 2px solid royalblue; display: inline-block; padding-bottom: 5px;">
							유형 02. 무리식
						</h4>
						<a href="/wiki/chapter01/types/type02/" class="problem-link">연습 ✏️</a>
					</div>
					<p>다음 극한값을 구하시오.</p>
					<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.4rem; margin: var(--base-grid) 0;">
						{limInf} { "$ (\\sqrt{x^2 + 2x} - x) $" }
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Type 03 -->
				<div class="type-section" id="type03">
					<div class="type-header" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 15px;">
						<h4 style="margin: 0; color: #1a1a1a; border-bottom: 2px solid royalblue; display: inline-block; padding-bottom: 5px;">
							유형 03. 미정계수
						</h4>
						<a href="/wiki/chapter01/types/type03/" class="problem-link">연습 ✏️</a>
					</div>
					<p>다음 등식이 성립하도록 하는 상수 $a, b$의 값을 구하시오.</p>
					<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.4rem; margin: var(--base-grid) 0;">
						{limInf} { "$ \\frac{ax^3 + bx^2 + 5}{x^2 - 1} = 3 $" }
					</p>
				</div>

				<a href="/wiki/chapter01/limits/" class="back-link">← 개념 공부로 돌아가기</a>
			</section>

			<div slot="summary">
				<p>무한대 극한의 핵심은 **'가장 힘이 센 항(최고차항)'**을 찾는 것입니다. 무리식이 있으면 유리화를 통해 우리가 아는 차수 비교 형태로 바꾸는 것이 전략입니다.</p>
			</div>
		</CornellNote>

		<script is:inline>
			document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
				renderMathInElement(document.body, {
					delimiters: [
						{left: '$$', right: '$$', display: true},
						{left: '$', right: '$', display: false}
					],
					throwOnError : false
				});
			});
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
